Python Zgoubi
By Sam Tygier Sam.Tygier@hep.manchester.ac.uk

This is an interface to zgoubi. It is tested with zgoubi 5.1.0 from http://sourceforge.net/projects/zgoubi/ on Linux.

Requirements
Python 2.5 or newer (not ported to 3.x yet)
Numpy 1.0 or newer
Scipy
Matplotlib

To install run
./setup.py install
or to in install to a specific place
./setup.py install --prefix=/home/sam/pyzgoubi


Documentation is avaliable at http://www.hep.man.ac.uk/u/sam/pyzgoubi/doc.html or in the doc/ directory.
To build the documentation run (you will need sphinx installed)

./setup.py build_doc

More information can be found at http://www.hep.man.ac.uk/u/sam/pyzgoubi/ or https://sourceforge.net/projects/pyzgoubi/



